# Privacy Policy of Raahi Music Bot

Effective Date: 01/01/2024 (DD/MM/YY)

## 1. Introduction

Welcome to Raahi! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the Raahi music bot ("Bot") on Discord. By using Raahi, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

## 2. Information We Collect

### 2.1 Personal Information

Raahi does not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or phone number. The Bot operates within Discord and does not require users to provide any personal details.

### 2.2 Usage Data

We may collect information about your interactions with Raahi, including:

- Commands used
- Music played
- Time and duration of usage
- Server information (e.g., server ID, channel ID)

This data helps us improve the Bot and provide a better user experience.

## 3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information collected for the following purposes:

- To provide and maintain the Bot's functionality
- To analyze usage trends and improve performance
- To troubleshoot and resolve issues
- To communicate updates and important information regarding the Bot

## 4. Data Retention

We do not store any personally identifiable information. Usage data may be retained for a limited time to help us improve the Bot, but it will not be linked to any individual user.

## 5. Data Security

We take data security seriously and implement reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.

## 6. Third-Party Services

Raahi may use third-party services for certain functionalities (e.g., music streaming). These services may have their own privacy policies, and we recommend reviewing them. We are not responsible for the content or practices of third-party services.

## 7. Children's Privacy

Raahi is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child, we will take steps to delete that information.

## 8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of significant changes through the Bot or via Discord. Your continued use of Raahi after any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

## 9. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Support Server](https://discord.com/invite/F3TQXtR6VF).

---

By using Raahi, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms. Thank you for using Raahi!
